snippet.title: Avatar: Fire and Ash | New Trailer
snippet.description:
This world is much deeper than you imagine. Watch the brand-new trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash and experience it in theatres December 19th.

Also, don‚Äôt miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

With ‚ÄúAvatar: Fire and Ash,‚Äù James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na‚Äôvi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na‚Äôvi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Salda√±a), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Joel David Moore, CCH Pounder, Edie Falco, David Thewlis, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, Britain Dalton, Jamie Flatters, Trinity Jo-Li Bliss, Jack Champion, Brendan Cowell, Bailey Bass, Filip Geljo, Duane Evans, Jr., and Kate Winslet.

#Bhammariya #GujaratiGarba #Garba2025 #NavratriSong #Dandiya2025 #NewGarbaSong #GujaratiSong2025

Welcome to the official release of "Bhammariya", the most energetic and soulful Gujarati Garba song of 2025! Get ready to immerse yourself in the vibrant spirit of Navratri, as this track brings you the perfect blend of traditional folk beats and modern production ‚Äì crafted specially for your Dandiya nights, Garba performances, and festive celebrations across the world.

"Bhammariya" is more than just a song ‚Äì it‚Äôs a celebration of Gujarat‚Äôs rich folk heritage, rhythmic beauty, and spiritual devotion to Maa Amba. Whether you're spinning around in a circle with your Garba group or dancing with dandiya sticks under the stars, this track is designed to elevate your festive experience!

Title: Bhammariya

Genre: Folk / Garba / Traditional

Release Year: 2025

Occasion: Navratri, Dandiya Raas, Festival, Cultural Events

Produced by: [Insert Producer or Production Company]

üéµ Traditional Vibes with a Modern Twist ‚Äì The rhythm stays true to Gujarati folk culture, while offering a sound that's fresh and energetic.
ü™ï Authentic Instrumentation ‚Äì From the dhol to the nagara, every beat is designed to make your feet move.

üíÉ High-Energy Dance Beats ‚Äì Boost your mood and your moves with fast-paced, festive dandiya beats.
üôè Spiritual Connection ‚Äì An ode to Maa Durga, evoking devotion and joy through rhythm and lyrics.

üìÖ When to Play Bhammariya:

During Navratri 2025 Garba events

snippet.title: I Went to FFMIC and Total Gaming Became CS Champion üèÜüî• Live Reaction üò≥
snippet.description:
Today, I witnessed one of the best comebacks in Free Fire history! After four years, the Free Fire India Max Cup returned, and Total Gaming pulled off an epic BOOYAH! In the finals against GodL, GodL had a 2-point lead in the best-of-five series. But Total Gaming made an incredible comeback, leveling the score 2-2. In the final match, with the score tied 5-5, Total Gaming clinched the victory in the last round. It was truly an epic comeback and one of the greatest moments in Free Fire‚Äôs history!

A big shoutout and congratulations to Ajju Bhai, Total Gaming, Fauji ajay mafia and Delete & all for their outstanding performance! Also, kudos to Jonty Gaming and NG Pros for their amazing gameplay. And let‚Äôs not forget Marco from the GodL team, whose sniping was absolutely top notch!

All the best to everyone in the battle royale matches today

We‚Äôre updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more!

snippet.title: MIBR vs. NRG ‚Äî VALORANT Champions Paris ‚Äî Playoffs Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world‚Äôs top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We‚Äôre proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports
Facebook: /valorantesports
Instagram: @valorantesports
TikTok: @valorantesports
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/valorant
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@ValorantEsports

snippet.description:
Song Credits:
Song: Choli Ke Peeche Kya Hai 
Movie:  Khal Nayak (1993)
Singer: Alka Yagnik & Ila Arun
Composer: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi

Movie Credits:
Cast : Sanjay Dutt, Jackie Shroff, Madhuri Dixit, Raakhee, Anupam Kher
Director : Subhash Ghai
Producer : Subhash Ghai

Lyrics:

Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶
Choli Ke Peechhe Kya Hai,
Choli Ke Peechhe
Choli Ke Peechhe Kya Hai,
Choli Ke Peechhe
Chunari Ke Niche Kya Hai,
Chunari Ke Niche

Ho Choli Mein Dil Hai Mera,
Chunari Mein Dil Hai Mera
Choli Mein Dil Hai Mera,
Chunari Mein Dil Hai Mera
Yeh Dil Mein Dungi Mere Yar Ko, Pyar Ko
Aah Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Are Lakhon Deewane Tere, Lakhon Deewane
Aashiq Purane Tere, Aashiq Purane
Ho Aashiq Mila Naa Aisa Hmmm,
Meri Pasand Jaisa Hmmm
Be Dil Shahar Yeh Aisa,
Kya Karu Kya Karu
Hay Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶
Resham Kaa Lahanga Meraa,
Resham Kaa Lahanga
Lahanga Hai Mahanga Meraa,
Ahanga Hai Mahanga
Lahanga Utha Ke Chalu,
Ghunghat Gira Ke Chalu
Kya Kya Bacha Ke Chalu Ramaji Ramaji

Are Isako Bachalo Babu, Iss Ko Bachalo
Dil Me Chhupalo Babu, Dil Mein Chhupalo
Ho Aashiq Pade Hain Pichhe O Ho
Koyi Idhar Ko Khinche Hmmm
Koyi Udhar Ko Khinche Kya Karu Kya Karu
Hay Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶
Hai Shadi Karado Meri O Ho,
Shadi Karado Hmmm
Doli Sajado Meri Doli
Saja Do Ah Ha Ah Ha
Sautan Bana Naa Jaye,
Jogan Bana Naa Jaye
Joban Saha Naa Jaye
Kya Karu, Kya Karu Hai Chhori
Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Are Ladaki Ho Kaisi Bolo,
Ladaki Ho Kaisi
Ladaka Ho Kaisa Bolo
Ladaka Ho Kaisa
Ho Ladaki Ho Mere Jaisi Aah Ha,
Ladaka Ho Tere Jaisa Wah Wah
Aaye Maja Phir Kaisa,
Pyar Kaa Pyar Kaa Wah
Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶
Ho‚Ä¶Jhumari Kaa Jumaru Ban Ja,
Jhumari Kaa Jumaru Kich Kich
Payal Kaa, Ghungharu Ban Ja
Payal Kaa Ghungaru Kich Kich
Meri Salami Kar Le, Meri Ghulami Kar Le
Hoga Too Hoga Koyi
Badashah, Badashah Are Jan
Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Bali Umariya Meri Bali Umariya
Suni Sajariya Meri Suni Sajariya
Mere Sapano Ke Raja,
Jaldi Se Vapas Aaja Ah
Soti Hoon Main
Daravaja Khol Ke, Khol Ke Ah
Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶
